OL,3,CLinda Nolan opens up about how her
OL,4,Ccancer diagnosis has stopped her
OL,5,Cperforming
OL,7,FLinda Nolan says she is trying to
OL,8,Fmake memories every day, as the
OL,9,Fsinger lifts the lid on her battle
OL,10,Fwith cancer.
OL,12,FThe 64-year-old, who rose to fame as
OL,13,Fone of the Nolan sisters, was first
OL,14,Fdiagnosed with breast cancer in 2006.
OL,16,FNolan, whose group had a hit in 1979
OL,17,Fwith I'm In The Mood For Dancing,
OL,18,Fsaid: "The last results were
OL,19,Fpromising but the results before that
OL,20,Fwhen it had spread to my brain were a
OL,21,Freal kick to the stomach.
